Package mklab.JGNN.data.datasets

Class Dataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • mklab.JGNN.data.datasets.Dataset
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Datasets.Adult, Datasets.BreastCancer, Datasets.CALLS, Datasets.CiteSeer, Datasets.Cora, Datasets.CoraGraph, Datasets.ENRON, Datasets.FRIENDS, Datasets.Lymphography, Datasets.MESSAGES, Datasets.MUTAG, Datasets.PubMed, Datasets.SMS
    public class Dataset
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides automatic downloading and importing of well-known public datasets. These can be used to test amchine learning algorithms developed with JGNN. If you use the provided datasets for publication, please follow the links outputted by the library to the error console to find attribution requirements.
    Author:
    Emmanouil Krasanakis
